I"b<p>(MIT) Escreva um programa que conte o número de vogais numa <em>string</em> <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">s</code> composta unicamente de letras minúsculas. Por exemplo, se <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">s = 'azcbobobegghakl'</code>, seu programa deve imprimir <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">Número de vogais: 5</code>.</p>

<!-- more -->

<h3 id="solução">Solução:</h3>
<div class="language-python highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="n">s</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="nf">input</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="sh">'</span><span class="s">Digite uma string de letras minúsculas: </span><span class="sh">'</span><span class="p">)</span>

<span class="n">n</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="mi">0</span>
<span class="n">v</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="sh">'</span><span class="s">aeiou</span><span class="sh">'</span>

<span class="k">for</span> <span class="n">letter</span> <span class="ow">in</span> <span class="n">s</span><span class="p">:</span>
  <span class="k">if</span> <span class="n">letter</span> <span class="ow">in</span> <span class="n">v</span><span class="p">:</span>
    <span class="n">n</span> <span class="o">+=</span> <span class="mi">1</span>

<span class="nf">print</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="sa">f</span><span class="sh">'</span><span class="s">Número de vogais: </span><span class="si">{</span><span class="n">n</span><span class="si">}</span><span class="sh">'</span><span class="p">)</span>
</code></pre></div></div>
